data.description: Look no longer. This bigger-than-life home is now yours for the taking. The oversized home has three levels and the loft space to use as you need to. The main suite has its own floor for extra privacy. The open family room to the kitchen and eat-in is more than enough space for a growing or large family. The home has a covered front and back porch that loves to see summer tea days and cozy hot chocolate nights. All that is missing is your family and the added TLC the home needs and memories for your family. The home is AS-IS and all owner-occupants will get a home warranty of the buyer's choice not to exceed $600.
